description = 'Adventure Bar Labyrinth\nAdventure Bar Labyrinth is a rogue-like RPG that challenges you to tackle an unknown\ndungeon. To bring back the legendary treasure, you’ll need to enter the depths of the\ndungeon, find weapons and shields, and use magic rods and potions to fight against\nmonsters and raise your level.\n\nEach time you enter the dungeon, its structure changes along with the items and monsters\nwithin it. You can challenge the dungeon again and again, even if you’ve already cleared\nit. If you’re defeated, the items you obtain will all be lost, and your level will be\nreset to 1.\n\nThe ingredients you collect from the dungeon can be cooked in the bar to make food,\ngranting positive effects and EXP for the next adventure. Use all sorts of items to deal\nwith the monsters, find rare treasures and reveal the mystery of the labyrinth!\n\n2013 Rideon Japan\nNPPA00143'